title: "Events Page" menu option navigates to the Events page
custom_test_purpose:
Given I login as a verified patron with tickets
And I am navigated to the Events Page
And I click the "Invite People" button for an event
And I am navigated to the ticket details page
When I click the hamburger menu
And there is a menu option called "Events Page"
And I click the "Events Page" menu option
Then I am navigated back to the events page

title: Logout menu option text identifies Unverified patron's email address
custom_steps:
Given I login with as an Unverified Patron
When I click the hamburger menu
Then the "logout" menu option include the email address of the logged in patron

title: Logout menu option text identifies Verified patron's email address
custom_steps:
Given I login with as a verified patron
When I click the hamburger menu
Then the "logout" menu option include the email address of the logged in patron

title: Logout menu option logs out the patron
custom_steps:
Given I login with as a patron
When I click the hamburger menu
Then I can click the "logout" menu option to logout

title: "Group Tickets" text is clickable and navigates the user to the Events Page
custom_steps:
Given I login as a verified patron with tickets
And I am navigated to the Events Page
And I click the "Invite People" button for an event
And I am navigated to the ticket details page
When I click the Group Tickets text 
THen I am navigated back to the Events page
